3. cs.LG (Machine Learning): The paper discusses the use of synthetic data to facilitate the learning procedure of deep learning models, which falls under the category of machine learning. 
4. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence): The use of deep learning models for image classification and counting problems is a common application of artificial intelligence. 
5. cs.GR (Graphics): The generation of synthetic data involves the use of computer graphics techniques, which falls under the category of graphics.
